  "instructions": [
    "Roughly chop the onion, carrot, and celery.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, heat 2 tablespoons of oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery and sauté until they are tender.",
    "Add the garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the peppercorns and bay leaves and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cannellini beans, Shio-Koji Cured Pork Belly, thyme, and water to the Dutch oven.",
    "Stir to combine and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh parsley or thyme if desired."
